944
00:41:33,480 --> 00:41:34,400
Ya lo averiguaré

945
00:41:34,639 --> 00:41:35,679
Pronto te gustará.

946
00:41:42,119 --> 00:41:42,639
Entonces,

947
00:41:43,079 --> 00:41:44,000
¿Qué tan bueno es?

948
00:41:44,119 --> 00:41:45,760
¿Hay ingleses aquí?

949
00:41:46,239 --> 00:41:47,000
Honestamente,

950
00:41:47,000 --> 00:41:48,800
Solo los profesores están bien.

951
00:41:49,760 --> 00:41:50,719
Escuchaste a Cao Fan

952
00:41:50,719 --> 00:41:51,920
