956
00:41:57,239 --> 00:41:58,599
Probablemente yo sería igual de malo.

957
00:42:02,119 --> 00:42:02,599
Oh,

958
00:42:02,880 --> 00:42:03,920
verificar

959
00:42:04,239 --> 00:42:06,280
